high_descs: Turn to your right, go to the stove across the room.
Pick up the tea kettle on the rear left burner of the stove top.
Turn to your right, walk to the sink across the room.
Put the tea kettle under the faucet, turn the faucet on, fill tea kettle with water.
Turn the faucet off, pick up the kettle, turn around to your right, go to the stove across the room.
Place the kettle on the right front burner of the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Fill a tea kettle with water, put on stove top.

high_descs: Turn right and move towards and face the oven.
Pick up the tea kettle to the right of the bowl and from the top of the oven.
Turn right and move towards the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the tea kettle in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and pick up up the tea kettle from the sink.
Turn right, move forward towards the door, turn right again and move to the oven.
Place the tea kettle on front right burner on the top of the oven.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned tea kettle on an oven burner.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the stove.
Take the tea pot from the stove.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the tea pot into the sink, fill it with water, then take it back out.
Turn around and go back to the stove.
Put the tea pot back on the stove, on the right front burner.
anns.task_desc: Fill the tea pot with water.
